OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FRadio 2 presenter Steve    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FWright dies aged 69        
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, DJ Steve Wright, who presented         
OL,6, programmes for BBC Radio 1 and Radio 2 
OL,7, for more than four decades, has died at
OL,8, the age of 69.                         
OL,10,FHis family confirmed his death "with   
OL,11,Fdeep sorrow and profound regret" in a  
OL,12,Fstatement on Tuesday.                  
OL,14,FWright joined the BBC in the 1970s and 
OL,15,Fwent on to host the afternoon shows on 
OL,16,FRadio 1 and Radio 2.                   
OL,18,FHe also fronted television programmes  
OL,19,Ffor the BBC, including Top of the Pops.
